{"_path":"/_archieved/2020-06/punctuations","_dir":"2020-06","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"✒️ 关于标点的那些事儿","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"使用直排引号"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用直排引号"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"打代码的时候，频繁的中英文切换会导致输入效率降低，若一致使用英文标点（一个英文标点加一个空格）则可以增加编码速度。不过，习惯在编程时持续使用英文标点后，写博客时自然会保持这种惯性，这导致了我前期的博客页面崩坏——尽管版面的节奏要流畅许多，但英文标点在中文版面上的美观程度远远不及中文标点。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以上是我去年因为“使用英文标点”而产生的疑惑。现在来说，这个问题几乎已经算解决了：我现在已经习惯在中文输入时使用中文标点，而编码工作中尽量不使用中文。不过，现在，我又发现了一个新的问题，关于博客中的中文引号不美观的问题。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"起因"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"起因"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"应该有读者已经发现，我博客中引用的思源宋中的映射少了中文引号。这也就意味着，页面上所有中文引号，都会回退成其它字体引号的形态。见下图最后一行文字。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/200619/browser_06_20_003.png","alt":"页面上所有中文引号，都会回退成其它字体的引号"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这个引号可能来自某种英文非衬线体字体，看起来圆溜溜的，实在和思源宋不搭。接着我将博客中缺失的字体引用补充完整，界面成了这个样子："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"逗号加弯引号","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/200619/browser_06_20_012.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"引号依旧圆溜溜的。于是，我想着能不能换种特殊的字体，专门用来显示中文引号。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一番探索之后，我找到了“直角引号”这货。我决定把博客中所有的中文引号都替换成直角引号，以增加美观度。尽管两个邻接的逗号和直角引号间有空白过多之嫌，但比起逗号加弯引号要好多了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"直排引号","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/200619/browser_06_20_013.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“为什么在你的博客中要使用直排引号排版？”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“因为好看。”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“可是这样并不规范...”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“可是好看。”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"关于直角引号使用的规范，一般资料表示："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“竖排中文使用直角引号，横排文字使用弯引号”"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。不过在我个人的博客里，放弃使用弯引号并没什么可追究的。就像我喜欢用三点省略号作为全省略号的替代，直角引号配合中文方块字，也纯属喜好。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"hacker"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hacker"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其实，为了不更正我在中文输入中，从使用英文标点加空格到改为使用中文标点一贯以来的习惯。我在博客项目里，通过技术手段给弯引号加了魔法，使博客页面上的弯引号看起来是直角引号，而打字时，不用特意输入直角引号，直接 "},{"type":"element","tag":"keyboard","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Shift + \""}]},{"type":"text","value":" 打弯引号即可。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你可以在浏览器中按下 "},{"type":"element","tag":"keyboard","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ctrl + Shift + C"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 打开浏览器的控制台，再点击这段带有直接引号的 Hello World 查看页面原文："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“Hello World”"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，如果不会操作的话，可以参考下图。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"查看原文步骤","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/200619/06_20_007.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我给博客页面新增了一种字体，叫做“Quote”。这种字体内部只有“300C”、“300D”、“201C”、“201D”四种 Unicode 编码的字体图形映射，分别对应前直角引号，后直角引号，前弯引号和后弯引号。我通过工具把字体内部的弯引号的映射修改为映射到直角引号上，然后在页面中引用字体，所以页面上所有弯引号都渲染成了直角引号。对应的 CSS 样式见下："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{"className":"language-Stylus shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter github-light github-dark monokai","code":"/**************** 字体定义 */\n\nuseFontBaseURL(path) {\n    $font-url = 'https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/fonts/';\n    return url($font-url + path);\n}\n\n@font-face {\n    font-family: 'Quote';\n    src: useFontBaseURL('Noto_CJK_Quote/NotoQuote.woff2') format('woff2'), useFontBaseURL('Noto_CJK_Quote/NotoQuote.woff') format('woff'), useFontBaseURL('Noto_CJK_Quote/NotoQuote.ttf');\n    unicode-range: U+201c, U+201d, U+300C, U+300D;\n    font-display: block;\n}\n\n@font-face {\n    font-family: 'Noto Serif CJK';\n    src: ...\n}\n\n/**************** 字体引用 */\n\n:root {\n    --font-text: 'Quote', 'Noto Serif CJK';\n}\n\narticle {\n    font-family: var(--font-text);\n}\n","language":"Stylus","meta":"","style":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":1},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"/**************** 字体定义 */\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":2},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"emptyLinePlaceholder":true},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":3},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"useFontBaseURL(path) {\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":4},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"    $font-url = 'https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/fonts/';\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":5},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"    return url($font-url + path);\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":6},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"spa